  notes: 'Level adi: Level_23

    Boyut: 31x17

    Zorluk: Tum mekanikler 1

    Mekanik
    ozeti: Level 23 ilk tam kombinasyon: renk kilit, h1 plate, bridge, red break,
    ice, one-time ve jump. Donus looplari eklendi.

    Start koordinati: (1,15)

    Goal
    koordinati: (29,2)

    Renkli kilitler: YellowButton (21,10) link=G23 face=White;
    YellowDoor (25,14) link=G23 face=White; YellowButton (27,6) link=P23 face=Blue;
    YellowDoor (27,3) link=P23 face=Blue

    PressurePlate requiredFace bilgisi:
    (8,11) requiredFace=Red, mode=ActivateOnly, singleUse=False

    ToggleBridge
    bilgisi: (15,7) link=A23, startsActive=False

    OneTimeTile koordinatlari:
    (23,14) h0; (24,14) h0

    IceSlide rotalari: IceDownStart(17,7) -> IceMiddle(18,7)
    -> IceMiddle(19,7) -> IceLanding(20,7)

    GreenJump ve JumpLanding koordinatlari:
    Jump (27,10) h0; Landing (29,10) h0

    RedBreakable koordinatlari: (11,5) h0

    Gelistirici
    test cozum rotasi: Right, Right, Right, Right, Right, Right, Down, Down, Down,
